creator: American Music Company, Inc. Published by Ocean Life Music, BMI
title: Remembering The Helpers of 2017
description: We salute the helpers of 2017. When hurricanes and other tragedies kept coming, so did these brave, compassionate Americans. Their care and courage will be remembered.
